src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d68077b4ff908e70f2633d510669115b826bee76","tid":54479,"uid":68746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T15:09:47.000Z","msg":"仆街支那畜唔係乞就偷"},{"pid":"d882e75059b9a1b2f9dea07b15220869af269eb7","tid":54479,"uid":53322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T15:14:42.000Z","msg":"2005蘋果日報已經報導，十年了，政府都係懶理<br />\n<br />\n乞丐自由行<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n湖北省一位退休女幹部，兩年內四次共組織了二十四名婆婆來港行乞，她充當乞兒首領，每天賺到四百元的，給月薪二千，低於四百者，支薪一千。就這樣，她天天出動，送老丐到各個人流熱點打躉，扣除「工資」，這樣的「生意」，讓女幹部賺了八萬多元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/supplement/columnist/art/20050720/5064891\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fsupplement%2Fcolumnist%2Fart%2F20050720%2F5064891&d=G%2FjrA1oPeGwhof5TzPmtQoscwJTI%2BQouKF8MUrnyvY0%3D&h=02373970\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fsupplement%2Fcolumnist%2Fart%2F20050720%2F5064891&h=40efaf56\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/supplement/columnist/art/20050720/5064891</a>"},{"pid":"c6296e0ac93022a87c69099340aea16ac98b0404","tid":54479,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T16:13:02.000Z","msg":"聽講旅客區會有人主動趕，因為呢種區地產商要搵食，我想知真唔真？"},{"pid":"2b9acb7870373483345ba03ab3c988c7319f80ad","tid":54479,"uid":53322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T04:30:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聽講旅客區會有人主動趕，因為呢種區地產商要搵食，我想知真唔真？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔肯定，但我係IFC條天橋報過三，四次警，警察係比較有禮貌同快。<br />\n<br />\n而旺角就愛理理不理果種仆街態度。"}]}